data.description: Well, what do we have here? A home that is in nearly perfect condition and priced below $200,000… It's a unicorn!! This cozy 2 bd 1 bath ranch has been lovingly cared for and fully renovated in the recent past. Nearly everything was touched during the remodel work and since then the yard has been fenced & the carport with extra storage was added. The hardwood floors and stylish kitchen stand out, but everything else just as nice. If you want an efficient home that is ready for you to move in and love, this is the one you’ve been waiting for. You better get here fast, there aren't many out there that are in this good of condition. Call to schedule a private showing, TODAY!
